::DrillBit/KitKat2::

He got out of the CR chamber in time to see KitKat2 walking by. He ran
up.
"Hey hon." 
She turned to DrillBit.
"Thank god your back. I was getting worried."
"We had some problem but everything worked out ok," he said.

They both went off talking, as they looked for Killfest or anyone els.
